(185, 'Dán bảo vệ JCPal MacGuard MacBook Pro 13', '750000', '675000', 10, 'product-featured-185.png', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 21px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-weight: 700;\">Miếng dán bảo vệ JCPal MacGuard 5 trong 1 cho MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020 - Mỏng nhẹ & bảo vệ đầy vững chắc</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Nhằm gia tăng độ bảo vệ cho MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020 và giúp bạn yên tâm mang máy bất cứ đâu, hãy trang bị ngay phụ kiện </em><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">miếng dán bảo vệ JCPal MacGuard 5 trong 1 cho MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020.</em></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(54, 54, 54);\">Thiết kế 5 trong 1 với chất liệu polycarbonate linh hoạt</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/phu-kien/dan-man-hinh/dan-bao-ve-macbook-64.html\" title=\"Dán Macbook chính hãng\" target=\"_self\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(215, 0, 24); cursor: pointer;\">Miếng dán Macbook</a> bảo vệ JCPal MacGuard 5 trong 1 được thiết kế theo chuẩn thân máy MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020, nhờ đó mà miếng dán bao phủ toàn thân máy một cách vừa vặn & để lại khoảng trống phù hợp cho cổng sạc hoặc cổng USB.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">JCPal MacGuard bao bọc 5 bộ phận chính trên laptop gồm màn hình, mặt trên máy, mặt dưới máy, đệm kê tay và bàn rê chuột. Chất liệu polycarbonate linh hoạt cũng làm cho việc lắp đặt trở nên đơn giản hơn hết.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/x,webp,q100/media/wysiwyg/accessories/case/mieng-dan-bao-ve-jcpal-macguard-macbook-pro-13inch-2020-5-in-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thiết kế 5 trong 1 với chất liệu polycarbonate linh hoạt\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Miếng dán bảo vệ JCPal MacGuard 5 trong 1 có thiết kế mỏng chỉ 1.3mm cùng trọng lượng nhẹ nhàng, giúp tạo nên lớp bảo vệ tối ưu nhưng không gây nặng thêm cho máy. Phía dưới miếng dán còn có phần chân đế chống trơn, giúp cố định máy khi đặt lên bàn làm việc.</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(54, 54, 54);\">Chống thấm ẩm & trầy xước cao cấp cho MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Bảo vệ chính là điểm mấu chốt của miếng dán JCPal MacGuard 5 trong 1 cho MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020. Miếng dán này sẽ bảo vệ MacBook Pro 13 inch của bạn khỏi các vết trầy xước, vệt bắn nước và bụi bặm bám vào máy, giúp giữ cho máy luôn sạch sẽ như mới.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.cellphones.com.vn/x,webp,q100/media/wysiwyg/accessories/case/mieng-dan-bao-ve-jcpal-macguard-macbook-pro-13inch-2020-5-in-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chống thấm ẩm & trầy xước cao cấp cho MacBook Pro 13 inch 2020\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Nhờ được thiết kế dành riêng cho MacBook Pro 13 inch, miếng dán JCPal MacGuard 5 trong 1 sẽ bám dính vào máy mà không gây bong tróc. Với công nghệ iiEoue, miếng dán sẽ đảm bảo an toàn cho cả người dùng lẫn thiết bị.</p>', '', '<ul class=\"technical-content-modal\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; list-style: none; width: 500px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><li class=\"technical-content-modal-item m-3\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.75rem !important; padding: 0px;\"><p class=\"title is-6 m-2\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0.5rem !important; margin-right: 0.5rem !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem !important; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.125;\">Thông tin hãng</p><div class=\"modal-item-description mx-2\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-left: 0.5rem !important; margin-right: 0.5rem !important; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"px-3 py-2 is-flex is-align-items-center is-justify-content-space-between\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; justify-content: space-between !important; align-items: center !important; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem !important; display: flex !important; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><p style=\"box-